snippet.textDisplay: Allah means the one true God worthy of worship in arabic. We believe He sent many prophets and messengers, including Adam, Noah, Jacob, Isaac, Ishmail, Jesus, and Mohamed peace be upon them all. With the same message, worship one God and don't associate any partners with Him, and follow the teachings of the messenger sent for that time. If Moses was sent today we would follow him, as he would be the way to God. Muhammed pbuh is the last and final messenger, and he is our way to God and ultimately heaven.
